QuestData.Title: Warchief's Command: Howling Fjord!
QuestData.Description:
All able-bodied members of the Horde are hereby ordered to report to Apothecary Lysander in Howling Fjord.
The Forsaken have established a stronghold on the eastern shores of Northrend.
Now is the time to strike at the Scourge with our military might and a new plague that is being developed by the Royal Apothecary Society.
For the Horde!
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Apothecary Lysander in Howling Fjord.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak to Apothecary Lysander in Howling Fjord.
QuestData.RewardText: Ah, $n, you have arrived!$B$BLet's get to work.
